{"tid":462663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[光復旺角行人專用區] 不如組團去霸返平時啲大媽表演場地","createTime":"2017-11-08T18:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T16:15:37.000Z","uid":84037,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"12e40228d0753bc43f68f49ddfcf26c16389cfd0","tid":462663,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T18:00:46.000Z","msg":"西洋菜南街日日比班大媽拎嚟跳舞，住户行人都飽受其害<br />\n黑警唔做嘢，政府管唔掂<br />\n不如我地自己嚟<br />\n每到星期六日行人專用區開放嗰時，我地早過班大媽，靜坐霸住佢地平時嘅地頭，大家喺嗰度打機吹水做乜都好，總之就趕絕班大媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab9d3747ab1f1c5549332f6a31c2be50e971dc3","tid":462663,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T19:23:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49028c81cd678e5d469b5cb56392f0b01520cb26","tid":462663,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T20:20:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24b8e2f5eba622d118cf95c1838db8d4f0cc7b1b","tid":462663,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T21:09:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0b8119f70aff9a45f480a7d2c9f0ebc7e5720b6","tid":462663,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T21:30:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0bfbb942a24ce55dd1c6766ceee6f789f1c00b6","tid":462663,"uid":51302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T21:51:20.000Z","msg":"會唔會比黑底搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12261def1cbd2607998ace2f98cc559fe7b9a4b3","tid":462663,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T22:48:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會比黑底搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班大媽得啲廢中廢老撐 黑底點會同班大媽一堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c978f0d3a12e7719f4f19fceeb28cbae421102","tid":462663,"uid":32150,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T23:11:28.000Z","msg":